
THe ability to control media devices with a computer is very powerful.

This can let programs like XBMC turn off the TV during shutdown, or adjust the volume with an iPhone app.

THere are many IR blaster solutions out there, but they are over $20.  Using the ATMega8U2 MCU, it should be possible to create a USB IR blaster for around $10.

The biggest negative is that this IC only comes in surface mount so a PCB will have to be made.
